ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many weights is the woman holding?')

ANSWER7=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER2} xor {ANSWER5}')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER6} and {ANSWER7}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER8)
